190808*@   SMS발송 DATA FILE WRITE
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S4300-SMS-DATA-WRITE-RTN.

           INITIALIZE                  WK-D1-REC

      *   데이터구분
           MOVE  'DT'
             TO  WK-D1-DATA-DSTIC

           ADD   1
            TO   WK-J
      *   일련번호
           MOVE  WK-J
             TO  WK-D1-SERNO
      *   고객식별자
           MOVE  SPACE
             TO  WK-D1-CUST-IDNFR
      *   고객관리번호
           MOVE  SPACE
             TO  WK-D1-CUST-MGT-NO
      *   고객휴대폰번호
           MOVE  WK-IN-CPHN-NO
             TO  WK-D1-CUST-CPHN-NO
      *   고객명
           MOVE  WK-IN-CUST-NM
             TO  WK-D1-CUSTNM
      *   회신전화번호
210128     MOVE  WK-IN-RPLY-TELNO
             TO  WK-D1-RPLY-TELNO
      *   메시지내용(80 BYTE)
           STRING  '미등록상품이 존재합니다. '
                   '상품원장비교조회 확인바랍니다. '
                   '(04-3H-058)'
                   DELIMITED BY SIZE
           INTO  WK-D1-MSG-CTNT
      *   업무접수식별ID
           MOVE  SPACE
             TO  WK-D1-BZWK-RCEPT-IDNFI-ID
      *   발송부점코드
           MOVE  '4055'
             TO  WK-D1-SEND-BRNCD
      *   발송직원번호
           MOVE  CO-PGM-ID
             TO  WK-D1-SEND-EMPID

           WRITE   WK-O1-REC
           ADD     1                   TO    WK-WRITE-CNT
           ADD     1                   TO    WK-WRITE-CNT1
           .

       S4300-SMS-DATA-WRITE-EXT.
           EXIT.

